## Flujo ETL

```
scrape() → save_raw → process() → validate() → save_output
```

| Etapa | Archivo | Responsable |
|---|---|---|
| Extraccion | `src/<job>/scraper.py` | Data Engineer |
| Extraccion | `src/<job>/utils.py` | Data Engineer |
| Transformacion | `src/<job>/process.py` | Data Engineer |
| Configuracion | `src/<job>/settings.py` | Data Engineer |
| Configuracion web | `src/<job>/web_config.yaml` | Data Engineer |
| Validacion | `src/<job>/validate.py` | Gobierno de Datos |

